### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/split-pdf/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Split page range (needs ./samples/document.pdf)
POST {{baseUrl}}/split-pdf/split?mode=range&startPage=1&endPage=2
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=SplitBoundary

--SplitBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./samples/document.pdf
--SplitBoundary--

###

### Split every page as ZIP
POST {{baseUrl}}/split-pdf/split?mode=each
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=SplitBoundary

--SplitBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./samples/document.pdf
--SplitBoundary--
